<span id="Further_Sketcher_improvements"></span>
=== Autres améliorations de Sketcher ===

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* It is now possible to directly use external geometry as input for tools like offset or transform (array) [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/17615 Pull request #17615]
* The Sketcher axes are now displayed with infinite length. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/17312 Pull request #17312]
</div>

